commits.message:
Fix Local Currency Screen Crash (#355)

'viewLifecycleOwner' is tied to when the fragment has (and loses)
its UI (onCreateView(), onDestroyView()) whereas 'this' is tied 
to the fragment's overall lifecycle (onCreate(), onDestroy()), 
which may be substantially longer.

It is better to use the 'viewLifecycleOwner' but it has to be done 
in '(onViewCreated())' instead of in 'onCreate()'

Uphold: Fix send crashes and add logout timer (#356)

* Moved InteractionAwareActivity to 'common' module to use it in other submodules (ie uphold-integration).  This is for the logout timer.

* Fixed crash when manipulating UI elements after finishing Activity (in uphold-integration).

* Converted InteractionAwareActivity to Java since 'common' module doesn't support Kotlin
Update screenshots and remove obsolete images
Update app store icon to required format
Fix crash when starting blockchain service on new wallet (#357)
Use devnet flavor for palinka, evonet flavor for the public evonet

Evonet: Add Shortcut Button | Create Username (#342)

* Add 'Join DashPay' quick action (always visible)

* Add mock implementation of FundNewAccountActivity

* Hide 'Join DashPay' action when sync not completed and
when balance is bellow minimum DashPay user creation fee

* Removed obsolete SporkUpdatedEventListener
